[{"id":577946,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"<p>气味好大，但是跟她说了，又怕显得我小气。不说吧，感觉被熏得头晕晕的，有点想吐。怎么办？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577946","replies":94,"created_ts":1561607337,"created":"11:48:57","title":"对面桌的同事经常脱了鞋，还把脚伸到我桌面底下，该不该提醒一下它","author":"frozenway","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/frozenway","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c684/ffbb/226009_mini.png?m=1492142515"},{"id":577987,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1473710080","description":"<p>老哥生活在德国，对于垃圾分类这件事，也是从一开始的不习惯，到如今习以为常。</p>\n<p>看到另一个帖子里的人在完全不了解的情况下就各种喷，我看不太下去。</p>\n<p>德国的垃圾分类其实很简单。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>塑料类的扔黄色袋子，统一回收以后可以再次利用。要不然不停生产新的塑料，等着子孙后代被塑料淹没？</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>厨余有机垃圾，回发酵变臭的那种，不能焚烧，否则会降低温度释放二恶英。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>硬纸板，主要是大量的快递盒，都是可回收利用的。德国一天到晚都一堆 ebay 亚马逊的快速，更别说中国要用多少纸板。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>电子垃圾，还能用就挂 ebay 卖了，或者堆门口，约垃圾站的人来回收，再或者自己送垃圾站去。另外大家电，旧电池在电器卖场也可以回收。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>其他垃圾，以上分完还有剩的就扔其他。如果尽力分类了，其他垃圾一般很少。就算有也可以直接焚烧。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>总之我有点不解，9102 年了，自己一个异乡人都在努力爱护别人的家，自己人反倒还没意识到垃圾分类的重要性。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577987","replies":87,"created_ts":1561615919,"created":"14:11:59","title":"德国的垃圾分类","author":"linearxian","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/linearxian","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5c7cbf2ad73a4e0e130b5de9cd2fccdc?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577917,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"看到了巨大的差距，我却还在写着不重要的代码，过着不知道要干什么的日子。<br /><br />想离职了好好思考下未来的计划，考研？考雅思？还是去上海试一试？还是转行转业，找小伙伴一起做点什么<br /><br />哎，人生好难...","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577917","replies":84,"created_ts":1561604542,"created":"11:02:22","title":"堂姐被 Georgetown University 录取了","author":"yongzhong","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yongzhong","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/28c671cb0ad0b41e89368c524e4e42c6?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577990,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1523199974","description":"<p>现在看了下，便宜的有帝豪，英朗；稍微好点的卡罗拉不知道有没有国六，思域 1.0t 不知道够不够用。还有轩逸和朗逸。suv 不知道 H6 行不行。求各位大神给推荐车，指点一下。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577990","replies":71,"created_ts":1561616129,"created":"14:15:29","title":"新手买车，办齐价格希望控制在 9 到 14 万之间，咨询各位大神买什么车合适","author":"yngby","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yngby","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/98e976609411fd0d9b26307708be474a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577960,"node":"深圳","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1559027827","description":"之前发了个帖子去西藏，现在已经回来了，先分享几张图吧<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kUa4e2D.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kUa4e2D.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eOtx4sU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eOtx4sU.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IE2DgB4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IE2DgB4.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/syjH9eT.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/syjH9eT.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OBIiO3p.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OBIiO3p.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QfVJQ9v.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QfVJQ9v.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z3qoFYF.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z3qoFYF.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/pgNhthy.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pgNhthy.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />现在回来有一个多月，已经没有了上班的念头，在西丽开了一间烘焙工作室，欢迎在深圳的朋友过来闲聊扯淡<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkygenp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gkygenp.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/QIjpz5L.png\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QIjpz5L.png\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IQdGnzj.png\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IQdGnzj.png\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/HX5SwTk.png\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HX5SwTk.png\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XKvFkyU.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XKvFkyU.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/21mB0Yt.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/21mB0Yt.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a><br /><br />明年计划自驾再去趟新疆，有兴趣的朋友吗？<br />也可以加我的 vx<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZRKRDHv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZRKRDHv.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\"></a>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577960","replies":69,"created_ts":1561611242,"created":"12:54:02","title":"基本上结束了 8 年的程序生涯","author":"caiqh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/caiqh","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/359b/8db6/64714_mini.png?m=1552542245"},{"id":577842,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"<p>还是大多数人都这样？</p>\n<p>只是现在不开心，还是一直都这样？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577842","replies":62,"created_ts":1561586758,"created":"06:05:58","title":"只是我一个人感觉工作不开心吗？","author":"ericgui","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ericgui","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f91c/6b29/55150_mini.png?m=1559317585"},{"id":577997,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1561030542","description":"<p>做的比较偏，是做的 webgl，主要用的 three.js ，其他的引擎也写过 demo，现在的公司前景挺好的，就是工资有点低。想问一下北京的平均水平如何，是因为今年行情不好吗，还是说我自己太菜了，希望相关行业的给一点意见，我也给自己定个目标。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577997","replies":60,"created_ts":1561617744,"created":"14:42:24","title":"北京应届生 8K 什么水平","author":"PygmalionEffect","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/PygmalionEffect","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8426d305739d1f614f40882510e1ff00?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577864,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"<p>如果你是用户，在打开网页的时候要做什么，可以提升性能或者体验？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577864","replies":57,"created_ts":1561598264,"created":"09:17:44","title":"[前端] 面试被问到一个问题答不上来","author":"waiaan","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/waiaan","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9c5850dbe56430ca732fbe3569ddc3bb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":578131,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"<p>需求是这样的: 查询某个用户是否存在，GET users/zhangshan</p>\n<p>我这边使用的是 drf 框架，为了与框架统一，资源未找到返回的状态码都是 404。</p>\n<p>与我这边对接的是 java 后台，他们觉得返回 404 会被他们 try cache，认为是请求参数有问题或者 URL 出错，程序不往下走了，而返回 200，response 为空，程序会往下走，而且知道 zhangshan 这个对象为空。</p>\n<p>大家觉得资源不存在应该返回什么状态码呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/578131","replies":56,"created_ts":1561641604,"created":"21:20:04","title":"Restful API 资源未找到应该返回什么状态码？","author":"zuoakang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zuoakang","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c056/1174/303346_mini.png?m=1522376709"},{"id":577895,"node":"宠物","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/pet","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e223/0b85/509_mini.png?m=1515388901","description":"微博博主，B 站 up 主，微信公众号啥的都行，我是实在对这种小生物一知半解的，愁啊<br />我们家最近要搬家，还没装修的时候一只大猫在我们家房子底下的洞里下崽儿了，可能还往里挖了挖，五只小猫，现在大猫走了，只剩五只小猫了，现在都是半岁了<br />这么下去也不是办法，虽然我是狗派的，但是小猫总得有人管，真是甜蜜的负担啊？但我一头雾水真的不知道怎么下手，比如猫粮，超市就只卖一岁大的，总不能给半岁大的猫吃一岁的猫粮吧，但是又怕网上买不靠谱<br />想要不贴吧上看看精选帖咋养猫，突然想起百度把贴吧以前的内容都删了，现在真不知道该怎么办好了<br />是养熟一点不怕人了再去打疫苗好呢，还是先给打疫苗好呢，这些都不知道","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577895","replies":53,"created_ts":1561602285,"created":"10:24:45","title":"求获取养猫知识的途径","author":"legao5kzhen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/legao5kzhen","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f13ba6e7d443dbd8b69ee0270397471f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577832,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1561030542","description":"<p>突然想到这个问题。</p>\n<p>有时看见别人电脑代码，别人 IDE 字号大小和自己习惯不一样，蛮膈应的。</p>\n<p>同类的问题是，IDE 背景暗色与亮色[doge]</p>\n<p>(纯吐槽，毕竟能写好代码就行了嘛)</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577832","replies":53,"created_ts":1561566132,"created":"00:22:12","title":"敲代码时，喜欢 IDE 字号大一点还是小一点？","author":"suom","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/suom","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d6b3/0a58/257934_mini.png?m=1533318335"},{"id":578137,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1559539058","description":"现在买苹果表是个好选择嘛？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/578137","replies":52,"created_ts":1561643527,"created":"21:52:07","title":"不想带机械表了，苹果表大家觉得如何？","author":"mayshen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mayshen","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/afb6/3e7d/408837_mini.png?m=1560390016"},{"id":577949,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"有木有方案实现一台只支持电话、短信、邮件、支付宝的手机？<br /><br />临近毕业，整天有很多计划却总因为止不住玩手机而耽搁。<br />曾试着换用功能机，效果还不错，但是一旦遇到支付场景就呵呵。腾讯家的东西都可以舍弃但是唯独支付宝，不管是骑车还是饮食消费都避不开支付宝。<br />诸位大佬见多识广，有木有一种办法实现我的需求？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577949","replies":52,"created_ts":1561608040,"created":"12:00:40","title":"需要一台只能用支付宝的手机，怎么解决？","author":"ciaoly","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ciaoly","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9c093582211702a9f0217a1e97bbb15f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577945,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1559539058","description":"<p>如题，尤其是超高频的远距离拖动，如触摸板，那手指可能会抽筋。</p>\n<p>那些说触摸板超级好用的可能之前没用过好的笔记本触摸板，mac 的这个触摸板只能说和系统结合的很好，各种手势加上多点加上按压。但是说体验完爆鼠标的，我觉得有点过分了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577945","replies":51,"created_ts":1561607285,"created":"11:48:05","title":"虽然 mac 的触摸板体验业界领先，但是论完整体验还是远不如鼠标","author":"hfl1995","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hfl1995","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/35bf/bde0/161110_mini.png?m=1561085893"},{"id":578113,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"<p>用了这么久安卓，杀后台的问题一直存在，再怎么强悍的旗舰手机，用上一段时间后就出这问题</p>\n<p>用的一加 6，经常出现应用里要接收验证码，然后去短信里看下验证码，等返回来应用就被杀了，然后就又得重新接收验证码。刚才就是被这样连搞三次，心态崩了。</p>\n<p>想不明白去年上半年才发布的旗舰机，到了今年咋就变成这球样子了。</p>\n<p>手机上一共装了 131 个 app，95%都是 google play 里下载的，为什么要这么疯狂的杀后台，电池优化一直都关闭的。</p>\n<p>从刚开始用智能手机到现在，华为小米魅族一直到现在的一加统统都是这鬼样子，啥时候才能不这么疯狂杀后台？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/578113","replies":50,"created_ts":1561636103,"created":"19:48:23","title":"你们的安卓手机杀后台吗？？","author":"Danswerme","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Danswerme","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7460/e1cd/274090_mini.png?m=1535709980"},{"id":577846,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1561032004","description":"iPhonese 这么大的，一直等出二代，几年都没动静，寻安卓替代品","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577846","replies":48,"created_ts":1561590174,"created":"07:02:54","title":"安卓有小屏机","author":"annika","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/annika","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/965b9d9238c15af811aa396e55170cb4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":577847,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"楼上每天清晨噪音，居委会沟通 5 次无效。<br /><br />准备全方位打击楼上。<br /><br />除了震楼神器，大家还用过什么斗争手段？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/577847","replies":47,"created_ts":1561591287,"created":"07:21:27","title":"决定报复楼上","author":"qdwang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/qdwang","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4be3/f330/40309_mini.png?m=1557747990"}]